 Resume Getting Rejected by ATS?</h1><p class=\"text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto\">Paste your resume below — get an instant ATS score, see exactly what&#x27;s failing, and unlock AI-powered fixes tailored to your target job.</p><div class=\"mt-4 flex justify-center gap-6 text-sm text-gray-500\"><span>✓ Free diagnosis</span><span>✓ 2 free rewrites</span><span>✓ Full report $4.99</span></div></div><form class=\"bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-gray-200 p-6 md:p-8\"><div class=\"grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2\"><div><label class=\"block text-sm font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-2\">Your Resume</label><textarea placeholder=\"Paste your resume text here...\" rows=\"16\" class=\"w-full rounded-xl border border-gray-200 p-4 text-sm focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-400 resize-none placeholder:text-gray-400 disabled:bg-gray-50 disabled:text-gray-400\"></textarea></div><div><label class=\"block text-sm font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-2\">Job Description</label><textarea placeholder=\"Paste the job description here...\" rows=\"16\" class=\"w-full rounded-xl border border-gray-200 p-4 text-sm focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-400 resize-none placeholder:text-gray-400 disabled:bg-gray-50 disabled:text-gray-400\"></textarea></div></div><div class=\"mt-6 text-center\"><button type=\"submit\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-xl bg-blue-600 px-10 py-4 text-lg font-bold text-white hover:bg-blue-700 active:bg-blue-800 disabled:opacity-50 disabled:cursor-not-allowed transition-colors shadow-md\">Analyze My Resume →</button><p class=\"mt-3 text-xs text-gray-400\">Free analysis · No account required · Results in ~15 seconds</p></div></form><div class=\"mt-10 text-center\"><p class=\"text-sm text-gray-500\">Powered by Claude AI · Trusted by job seekers worldwide</p></div></div></main><!--$--><!--/$--><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/webpack-74c939c87fa0092a.js\" id=\"_R_\" async=\"\"></script><script>(self.__next_f=self.__next_f||[]).